name: "Butterfly woman 1" by Cinthia Ponce
description:
The butterfly is a symbol of immortality, rebirth and resurrection, but also of lightness, inconstancy and the ephemerality of joy and beauty. Because of its capacity for transformation, it embodies metamorphosis and the potentialities of being.

Image source: pexels Intervention, customization and collage of images. Conceptual art. With different editing tools.
